  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3557189/" class="title-link">常识有时候是件有趣的事儿</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3557189"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhangcanon/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2195632-37.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhangcanon/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">長良川</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-17"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-17 14:15:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3557189_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1.不伤手的立白洗衣粉 爵是古代饮酒器的通称。但是作为专名，爵是用来温酒的。它有三只脚，下面可以举火，有长长凸出以便倒酒。上古常用的饮酒器是觚和觯，战国后出现了椭圆形的杯，两边有弧形的耳。 现在问题来了，电视里演的那些先秦剧，常常是几个哥们煞有介事地拿着爵一饮...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3557189/#comments">(11回应)</a>
