  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1260142">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1260142/" class="title-link">关于孟姜女的名字</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1260142"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1060698/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1060698-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1060698/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">安然</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-12-15"
      class="main-meta">2007-12-15 15:48:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1260142_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  从小一直以为孟姜女姓孟.名姜女.今天看了书才知道自己错了这么久.  周代的姓氏制度和封制制度、宗法制度有密切联系。其中女子称姓、男子称氏。这是因为氏是用来“明贵贱”，姓是用来“别婚姻”的。二者作用不同.并且自上古起同姓不婚,所以妇女的姓比名更为重要。待嫁的女子如果...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1260142/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1260142_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1260142_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7207851">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7207851/" class="title-link">薇讀書——《中國古代文化常識》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7207851"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/56375881/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u56375881-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56375881/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Cassandra</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-11-24"
      class="main-meta">2014-11-24 15:02:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7207851_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  很像高中時語文老師講的文化常識教材。通過天文曆法、姓氏起源、節日民俗等全方位介紹中國古代的文化。五四之後中國漸漸西化，光榮的革命之路也將國人對自己民族的傳統文化拋之腦後。這本書對回顧歷史，學習國學都很有幫助，讀者諸君若有興趣，不妨一觀。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7207851_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7207851_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





